{
  "stem": "15193.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When then, they-- they came to us and we were interviewed again by the-- by the Scotland Yard to ascertain whether we were alien-- friendly aliens or enemy aliens.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They declared us to be friendly aliens.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they allowed us to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what they did, they packed up a truck, took us all women on a truck to nearby village.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a company like Campbell's Soup.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They made all kinds of canned food, and I-- and we were supposed to clean, peel the potatoes, peel the carrots, peel everything.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they would pay us and would give us room and board.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was the only one who said, no, I am not going to work here.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You can make money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How come that you don't want to work here?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said no, that's not my profession.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So the three girls again held onto me, and they said, if she doesn't work here, I'm not going to work here.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they took us back to London.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I applied for a millinery job, and I got an interview with a wholesale millinery company, Jewish people owning it, Mr.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And Mrs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So when she said, can you copy a hat?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I said, I will try.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she gave me a hood and asked me to copy that hat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And after finished, she threw it in the garbage.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was no good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then she gave me a hood and she said, you make whatever you want with that hood, and I--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hood is an unfinished hat, the raw material to make a hat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, and it was like a hood, you know, with the-- the brim and the top.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so she gave me that hat and I made what I wanted.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
